ESPResSo is maintained and developed mainly at the Institute for
Computational Physics at Stuttgart University, Germany, in the group
of Prof. Dr. Christian Holm (http://www.icp.uni-stuttgart.de).

Until 2010, ESPResSo was maintained and developed mainly at the
Max-Planck-Institute for Polymer Research in Mainz, Germany in the
group of Prof. Dr. Kurt Kremer.

The following people have contributed to ESPResSo:

